summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6269 for the improvement of 50th Ave. South from Renton Ave. South to South Roxbury St.; and certain other streets and avenues; by constructing sanitary sewers and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 91573, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
